token is a custodial, wrapped version of the Witnet coin managed by
the WitSwap plaform. The token is minted by the WitSwap team whenever
someone wants to convert WIT coins to eWIT tokens and kept in custody.

back to WIT coins. The intent of this token is to allow decentralized
trading on Ethereum DEXs and, in the future, to pay independent bridge
operators with it if they choose to accept it.
